Bootstrap: 
 a basic button:
 ex:
 <button type="button" class="btn-default btn">基本按钮</button>
 
 @2:
means: use the btn basic styles and  use the class .active can make button in active. 
 button:
 ex:
     <div class="container">
	  <h2>按钮</h2>
	  <p> .active 类表示按钮被点击:</p>            
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">默认按钮</button>      
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-default active ">点击激活的默认按钮</button>
	  <br><br>
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-info">信息按钮</button>      
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-info ">点击激活的信息按钮</button>
	</div>
	
	
	Disabled: 
	ex:
	   <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">
      默认按钮
   </button>
   <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" disabled="disabled">
      禁用按钮
   </button>
   
   Others ways use button:
        
<a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">链接</a>
<button class="btn btn-default" type="submit">按钮</button>
<input class="btn btn-default" type="button" value="输入">
<input class="btn btn-default" type="submit" value="提交">



   
   
	
